data.description: Great buy in the City of Glendora, Look no more!! This great quiet family friendly neighborhood is centrally located near grocery stores, shopping, dining, recreational parks, the foothills and 210/57 Fwy. As you walk in this cozy home an open living room that leads into a formal dining room. Open kitchen concept with plenty of room to modify. Additional bonus room can be used as you wish. Back yard features red bricks to host family gatherings and plenty of room for your gardening adventures.  With a little update and TLC this home will be ready for your family.. Schedule you’re viewing fast as this one won’t last....it is ready for a new family to come in and call it a home. … Buyer to verify Information.."
